longBusinessSummary: RBAZ Bancorp, Inc. operates as the bank holding company for Republic Bank of Arizona that provides various community banking products and services for individuals, businesses, and professionals in Arizona. The company offers various business and personal checking and savings accounts. It also provides business term, equipment, commercial real estate, and small business administration loans; accounts receivable financing services; and business lines of credit. In addition, the company offers debit, credit, and ATM cards; treasury management, remote deposit capture, merchant card processing, and not-for-profit program services; and online and mobile banking, ATM, courier, notary, wire transfer, official check, and night depository services. RBAZ Bancorp, Inc. was founded in 2007 and is based in Phoenix, Arizona.
